# 🌐 Enterprise Network Operations & Performance Analytics

### *A comprehensive SQL-based analytical platform for real-time network monitoring, incident management, security analytics, and bandwidth optimization*

<br/>

[📊 View KPIs](#-kpi-metrics) · [🗃️ Schema](#️-database-schema) · [🔍 Queries](#-query-categories) · [🛡️ Security](#️-security--anomaly-detection) · [📂 Structure](#-project-structure)

</div>

---

## 📌 Overview

**NetworkDB** is a production-grade relational database system built in **MySQL** to monitor, analyze, and optimize enterprise network infrastructure. It provides structured data storage and a rich SQL analytics layer covering everything from basic reporting to advanced window function analytics and real-time security anomaly detection.

```
NetworkDB
│
├── 6 Normalized Tables         — Zone · Device · Employee · NetworkLog · Incident · BandwidthUsage
├── 100+ Analytical Queries     — Across 5 complexity tiers
├── 20+ KPI Metrics             — Performance · Reliability · Security · User Behavior
└── 3 Network Zones             — Multi-zone monitoring with granular drill-down
```

---

## ✨ Features

| Feature | Description |
|---|---|
| 🖥️ **Device Monitoring** | Track CPU, memory, uptime, and connection health per device |
| 📡 **Zone Analytics** | Latency, usage, and incident breakdown across 3 network zones |
| 🔐 **Security Detection** | Night-time access, data spike anomalies, multi-device fraud patterns |
| 📉 **Bandwidth Planning** | Daily/peak usage trends for capacity forecasting |
| 👤 **User Behavior** | Per-employee data usage, VPN ratio, off-hours access detection |
| ⏱️ **Incident SLA Tracking** | MTTR, MTBF, downtime duration, and severity classification |
| 🪟 **Window Functions** | RANK, LAG/LEAD, NTILE, PERCENT_RANK, cumulative analytics |
| 📊 **KPI Dashboards** | 20+ computed KPIs ready for BI tool integration |

---

## 🗃️ Database Schema

```sql
CREATE DATABASE NetworkDb;
USE NetworkDb;
```

### Entity Relationship Diagram

```
                    ┌─────────────────┐
                    │      ZONE       │
                    │─────────────────│
                    │ ZoneID (PK)     │
                    │ ZoneName        │
                    │ Location        │
                    └────────┬────────┘
                             │ 1:M              1:M
              ┌──────────────┤          ┌─────────────────────┐
              ▼              ▼          │   BANDWIDTH USAGE   │
   ┌─────────────────┐                  │─────────────────────│
   │     DEVICE      │                  │ UsageID (PK)        │
   │─────────────────│                  │ ZoneID  (FK)        │
   │ DeviceID (PK)   │                  │ Date                │
   │ ZoneID   (FK) ──┘                  │ TotalUsageGB        │
   │ DeviceType      │                  │ PeakUsageGB         │
   │ IPAddress       │                  └─────────────────────┘
   │ Status          │
   │ CPU_Usage       │◄──────────────────────────────┐
   │ Memory_Usage    │                               │
   │ UptimeDays      │ 1:M                      1:M  │
   └────────┬────────┘                               │
            │                                        │
    ┌───────┴────────┐              ┌────────────────┴───────┐
    │   INCIDENT     │              │      NETWORKLOG        │
    │────────────────│              │────────────────────────│
    │ IncidentID(PK) │              │ LogID      (PK BIGINT) │
    │ DeviceID  (FK) │              │ DeviceID   (FK)        │
    │ IncidentType   │              │ EmployeeID (FK) ───────►──────────┐
    │ StartTime      │              │ Timestamp              │          │
    │ EndTime        │              │ DataUsageMB            │  ┌───────┴──────────┐
    │ Severity       │              │ LatencyMS              │  │    EMPLOYEE      │
    └────────────────┘              │ AccessType             │  │──────────────────│
                                    │ Status                 │  │ EmployeeID (PK)  │
