## 🗂️ Project Structure

```
NetworkDB/
│
├── 📄 database_and_tables.sql    ← CREATE DATABASE + all 6 table definitions
│
├── 📄 queries.sql                ← 100 analytical queries (Q1–Q100)
│   ├── Q1–Q20   Basic SELECT     (filtering, sorting, simple lookups)
│   ├── Q21–Q40  JOIN Queries     (multi-table, LEFT JOIN, 4-table joins)
│   ├── Q41–Q60  Aggregation      (GROUP BY, HAVING, aggregate functions)
│   ├── Q61–Q80  Window Functions (RANK, LAG, NTILE, running totals)
│   └── Q81–Q100 Security/Anomaly (fraud detection, spike analysis)
│
├── 📄 kpis.sql                   ← 20+ KPI queries for dashboards
│   ├── Network Performance KPIs  (latency, availability, success rate)
│   ├── Incident & Reliability    (MTTR, MTBF, severity rates)
│   ├── User Behavior KPIs        (VPN ratio, off-hours, top consumers)
│   ├── Zone-Level KPIs           (per-zone latency, usage, incidents)
│   ├── Device Performance KPIs   (utilization, failure rate, high latency)
│   └── Security & Fraud KPIs     (suspicious activity, multi-device risk)
│
└── 📊 Table_connection_diagram.png  ← Visual ER diagram
```

