## 🤝 Contributing

Contributions are welcome! To add new queries or KPIs:

1. Fork the repository
2. Create a feature branch: `git checkout -b feature/new-analytics`
3. Add your query to the appropriate `.sql` file with a comment header:
   ```sql
   -- Q101. <Title>
   -- Purpose: <Description>
   SELECT ...
   ```
4. Open a Pull Request

